1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,920
[#TheMaskedHearts #Thotsakan]

2
00:00:07,080 --> 00:00:08,240
My name is Charm,

3
00:00:08,270 --> 00:00:10,880
the drummer
for my school's Khon Club.

4
00:00:11,240 --> 00:00:13,080
Khon is a classical Thai dance drama.

5
00:00:13,120 --> 00:00:15,940
It involves very strict movements
that you have to follow.

6
00:00:16,320 --> 00:00:18,440
However, there are troublemakers

7
00:00:20,160 --> 00:00:22,560
who insist on performing Khon
in their own way.

8
00:00:27,380 --> 00:00:31,840
This whole thing started
because of one edgy, macho guy.

9
00:00:39,880 --> 00:00:44,080
[Tanakorn Chuen-arom as Saen/Sand]

10
00:00:44,280 --> 00:00:48,840
[Wacharathon Wongyai as Rak/Lucky]

11
00:00:49,160 --> 00:00:52,960
[Worachai Areewong as Tan/Thank]

12
00:00:53,320 --> 00:00:58,040
[Khitaphat Choothai as Chim/Charm]

13
00:00:58,240 --> 00:01:01,640
[Kornkamon Supaseripap as Vila/ViVi]

14
00:01:01,920 --> 00:01:05,900
[Rungtiva Sangngoen as Prink
Napat Seela as Rit/Ton]

15
00:01:06,080 --> 00:01:09,480
[Chalisa Schaub as Kamala
Weeraachai Hatgovit as Phraya Banleng]

16
00:01:09,640 --> 00:01:13,840
[Nithiroj Simakamtorn as Phraya Dechanarong
Rattanachai Phakdirat as Khon Master]

17
00:02:38,020 --> 00:02:40,200
Blazing with fiery wrath.

18
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:42,400
A fierce flame burned in his scarlet eyes.

19
00:02:43,160 --> 00:02:45,400
His mighty power
spread across the three realms.

20
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:49,480
This is the beginning
of an edgy role-playing guy

21
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:51,720
who wants to become the legendary giant.

22
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:56,280
Welcome to
Sand's cringeworthy world as Thotsakan.

23
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:11,960
Hey.

24
00:03:13,380 --> 00:03:14,280
Hey!

25
00:03:14,870 --> 00:03:16,170
Do you need anything?

26
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:21,160
I wanna be as cool as him
when he plays Thotsakan.

27
00:03:21,740 --> 00:03:23,040
Have some respect.

28
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:24,880
This is Master Banleng,
our national artist.

29
00:03:26,420 --> 00:03:27,320
Hey, kid.

30
00:03:27,780 --> 00:03:31,200
Anyone can be Thotsakan.

31
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:35,930
Anyone can be Thotsakan.

32
00:03:36,420 --> 00:03:38,280
Since then, this edgy guy

33
00:03:38,300 --> 00:03:40,140
has always wanted to be Thotsakan
in his own way,

34
00:03:40,160 --> 00:03:41,780
for no good reason.

35
00:03:46,440 --> 00:03:48,720
All of you, dance with me.

36
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:49,880
Now.

37
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:53,190
This is the Phranluang rehearsal space,

38
00:03:53,220 --> 00:03:54,910
maintained by
the Department of Royal Entertainments.

39
00:03:54,950 --> 00:03:57,240
It was established
during the reign of the current monarch.

40
00:03:57,380 --> 00:04:00,960
I am Chim, a student of Phranluang,
serving in the Piphat ensemble.

41
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,960
I play the thap drum for the Khon dancers,

42
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,990
most of whom are the children of noblemen.

43
00:04:05,030 --> 00:04:06,920
All parents pray for their children
to become Khon dancers.

44
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:08,720
Very well. Go and practice by yourselves.

45
00:04:12,780 --> 00:04:15,800
This is Master Rit,
a man born of noble blood.

46
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:17,640
His father serves as a Phraya
in the Department of Royal Entertainments.

47
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:20,020
He is assured of the role of Thotsakan,

48
00:04:20,060 --> 00:04:22,040
unless some mishap occurs.

49
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:28,000
That is Saen, a companion of mine.

50
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:30,840
He is Master Rit's servant.

51
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:34,280
Water, Master.

52
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:38,440
He aspires to become Thotsakan.

53
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:40,520
His ambitions soar high indeed.

54
00:04:41,300 --> 00:04:44,720
Born a servant,
how else could he leave this world?

55
00:04:46,640 --> 00:04:49,520
However, His Majesty once composed:

56
00:04:50,460 --> 00:04:53,200
"Even the unattainable
may capture the heart.

57
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:55,920
To attain it, one must dare to ascend."

58
00:04:55,960 --> 00:04:58,720
I dare say he believes in those words.

59
00:05:13,880 --> 00:05:14,800
Master Rit.

60
00:05:16,400 --> 00:05:18,120
Prink bids me deliver this to you.

61
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:22,560
[My Beloved Rit, I must inform you
that my health has been failing of late,]

62
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:24,200
[and I am obliged to take strict rest.
Pray, do not be troubled.]

63
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,840
[Yours most affectionately, Prink]

64
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:31,720
What is the matter?

65
00:05:31,760 --> 00:05:33,680
Prink has taken ill. I must go.

66
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:35,880
But you are to perform.

67
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,480
Nothing holds greater importance
than my love.

68
00:05:39,320 --> 00:05:40,880
But your father will be in attendance.

69
00:05:41,840 --> 00:05:43,080
If he should learn that you...

70
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:44,280
You shall perform in my stead.

71
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:46,800
You are more skilled than I.

72
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:49,200
No. I am not...

73
00:05:51,640 --> 00:05:53,720
No one shall know
it is you beneath the mask.

74
00:05:54,820 --> 00:05:56,200
Consider it an act of aid to me.

75
00:06:03,420 --> 00:06:05,000
I remember that day well.

76
00:06:06,060 --> 00:06:10,280
Never had Saen feared anyone
more than Phraya Banleng.

77
00:06:10,320 --> 00:06:11,960
His own master.

78
00:06:22,440 --> 00:06:24,640
[Phranluang School]

79
00:07:40,460 --> 00:07:41,800
Good day, Rit.

80
00:07:42,260 --> 00:07:44,120
Do you remember me, Rak?
Your little brother?

81
00:07:44,540 --> 00:07:46,040
I came without your knowledge.

82
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:49,800
In Western lands,
this is called a surprise.

83
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:54,280
Four years ago,
Master Rak departed to study abroad.

84
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:55,800
He has grown dignified indeed.

85
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:58,000
His eyes and voice

86
00:07:58,320 --> 00:08:00,160
carry a warmth that soothes the heart.

87
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:12,720
Has Rit ever been so good at this?

88
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:16,560
In the span of four years,
he has changed considerably.

89
00:08:27,930 --> 00:08:28,930
Saen,

90
00:08:29,410 --> 00:08:30,730
am I doing this correctly?

91
00:08:31,810 --> 00:08:33,050
Yes, Master.

92
00:08:33,670 --> 00:08:35,230
If I may, you should hold your chest
a little higher.

93
00:08:44,450 --> 00:08:46,930
Did anyone find out about last night?

94
00:08:49,450 --> 00:08:50,690
I do not know.

95
00:08:53,170 --> 00:08:54,070
Rit.

96
00:08:58,690 --> 00:09:00,010
Of what are you speaking?

97
00:09:01,850 --> 00:09:02,850
Rak?

98
00:09:03,710 --> 00:09:05,210
We met last night.

99
00:09:08,650 --> 00:09:10,090
Or have you forgotten already?

100
00:09:17,490 --> 00:09:19,170
I wish to practice the rising movement.

101
00:09:20,470 --> 00:09:22,180
But you must be tired.

102
00:09:24,110 --> 00:09:28,290
May I have the use of Saen for a time?

103
00:09:31,150 --> 00:09:33,030
From his manner,

104
00:09:34,230 --> 00:09:36,610
he appears as capable
as any amateur Khon dancer.

105
00:09:39,330 --> 00:09:41,070
As you wish.

106
00:09:41,750 --> 00:09:43,770
Saen, be off with him.

107
00:10:22,430 --> 00:10:26,130
I do not know why my heart is pounding.

108
00:10:27,990 --> 00:10:29,550
His perfumed water.

109
00:10:30,470 --> 00:10:32,490
The sound of his breathing.

110
00:10:35,750 --> 00:10:37,410
Don't press so close to my waist.

111
00:10:38,570 --> 00:10:39,770
My apologies, Master Rak.

112
00:10:39,810 --> 00:10:40,930
I did not intend to.

113
00:10:52,890 --> 00:10:54,090
Be careful, Saen.

114
00:10:54,490 --> 00:10:56,250
Do not let my brother fall,

115
00:10:56,610 --> 00:10:57,970
or you shall answer for it.

116
00:11:00,510 --> 00:11:01,450
Yes, Master.

117
00:11:07,870 --> 00:11:09,490
Let us wait and see.

118
00:11:36,590 --> 00:11:37,890
Saen, what are you doing?

119
00:11:40,390 --> 00:11:41,770
I did not intend to.

120
00:11:42,970 --> 00:11:46,380
In Western lands,
such matters are spoken of more freely.

121
00:11:46,730 --> 00:11:48,190
But they don't do so in public.

122
00:11:49,750 --> 00:11:51,490
If you wish to do this later,

123
00:11:51,970 --> 00:11:53,250
do so in private.

124
00:11:54,430 --> 00:11:56,090
If Rit's room is not suitable,

125
00:11:57,530 --> 00:11:58,820
you may use mine.

126
00:12:00,330 --> 00:12:02,170
I did not mean it so.

127
00:12:16,830 --> 00:12:17,890
Come here.

128
00:12:19,070 --> 00:12:20,450
After a long journey

129
00:12:21,390 --> 00:12:23,090
and practice, I am weary.

130
00:12:41,710 --> 00:12:43,330
You may press more firmly.

131
00:12:44,430 --> 00:12:45,770
Do not worry about hurting me.

132
00:12:47,150 --> 00:12:49,210
I fear I may bruise you.

133
00:12:49,990 --> 00:12:51,350
You've practiced all day.

134
00:12:52,590 --> 00:12:54,090
I fear that being too rough

135
00:12:54,670 --> 00:12:56,290
may cause you pain.

136
00:13:03,930 --> 00:13:05,850
If you won't do it,

137
00:13:08,110 --> 00:13:10,930
I shall ask another servant.

138
00:13:20,790 --> 00:13:22,210
How very foolish you are.

139
00:13:28,970 --> 00:13:30,810
Yes, I am foolish.

140
00:13:31,170 --> 00:13:32,490
I confess as much.

141
00:13:33,670 --> 00:13:35,450
Foolish and ignorant,

142
00:13:35,630 --> 00:13:37,450
knowing full well that he is my master.

143
00:13:44,790 --> 00:13:47,330
Dignified and kind.

144
00:13:49,990 --> 00:13:51,610
My Rama.

145
00:13:57,670 --> 00:13:58,890
Last night,

146
00:14:01,270 --> 00:14:03,730
the man behind the Thotsakan mask...

147
00:14:05,850 --> 00:14:07,250
was it you?

148
00:14:11,710 --> 00:14:12,890
I...

149
00:14:13,590 --> 00:14:15,010
So you dare not say it?

150
00:14:16,830 --> 00:14:19,290
You must be very loyal to Rit.

151
00:14:23,030 --> 00:14:25,170
Then I shall ask him

152
00:14:26,010 --> 00:14:27,970
to place you in my service.

153
00:14:31,430 --> 00:14:33,050
Perhaps,

154
00:14:33,890 --> 00:14:35,650
if you consider me your master,

155
00:14:37,070 --> 00:14:39,370
you may speak more freely.

156
00:15:01,030 --> 00:15:01,740
Rit.

157
00:15:05,450 --> 00:15:06,570
What is the matter?

158
00:15:10,290 --> 00:15:12,170
I must speak with you about something.

159
00:15:13,030 --> 00:15:14,150
What is it?

160
00:15:16,650 --> 00:15:19,050
I wish to have Saen in my service.

161
00:15:22,090 --> 00:15:24,290
And what of me, then?

162
00:15:25,470 --> 00:15:27,690
You may request another servant.

163
00:15:28,270 --> 00:15:30,410
I have but recently returned from abroad

164
00:15:31,090 --> 00:15:32,690
and arrived in Phranluang.

165
00:15:33,210 --> 00:15:35,290
I do not know much
about the customs here.

166
00:15:36,230 --> 00:15:37,810
Saen has lived here a long time.

167
00:15:38,370 --> 00:15:39,680
He must know it well.

168
00:15:43,530 --> 00:15:44,530
Saen.

169
00:15:45,870 --> 00:15:47,170
Do you wish to go with him?

170
00:15:50,930 --> 00:15:52,370
As you wish, Master Rit.

171
00:15:53,110 --> 00:15:54,110
Very well, then.

172
00:15:54,730 --> 00:15:56,210
You may do so, if you wish.

173
00:15:57,050 --> 00:15:58,930
See that you serve him well.

174
00:15:58,970 --> 00:16:00,050
Do you understand?

175
00:16:01,330 --> 00:16:02,290
Yes, Master.

176
00:16:04,210 --> 00:16:06,130
I shall do my best to serve Master Rak.

177
00:16:30,540 --> 00:16:32,340
May I ask you, Rit?

178
00:16:33,260 --> 00:16:35,100
When shall I hold my grandchild?

179
00:16:37,640 --> 00:16:39,140
Well, Mother.

180
00:16:39,460 --> 00:16:42,100
The moment Rak returned,
you began pressing me.

181
00:16:42,740 --> 00:16:45,220
Why do you not advise him
to find a wife as well?

182
00:16:45,560 --> 00:16:48,220
But you are the elder brother.

183
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:50,660
Do not turn this upon him.

184
00:16:50,820 --> 00:16:52,620
Passing the blame back and forth.

185
00:16:52,660 --> 00:16:56,180
Be careful,
for you will become an old bachelor.

186
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:59,820
To be an old bachelor is not half bad.

187
00:17:00,020 --> 00:17:02,060
I shall remain to keep my mother company.

188
00:17:03,900 --> 00:17:05,700
You are very sweet with your words.

189
00:17:06,260 --> 00:17:08,160
Of course I am, Mother.

190
00:17:08,600 --> 00:17:11,580
If you drive me from this house,
how am I to live?

191
00:17:12,240 --> 00:17:13,420
I shall never wed.

192
00:17:13,660 --> 00:17:15,660
I shall keep you company forever.

193
00:17:20,020 --> 00:17:22,660
You need not trouble yourself
over his marriage.

194
00:17:23,560 --> 00:17:26,220
As soon as Rit becomes the understudy,

195
00:17:27,080 --> 00:17:30,820
I shall take matters into my own hands.

196
00:17:34,760 --> 00:17:37,860
After the next amateur Khon performance,

197
00:17:38,540 --> 00:17:41,260
I shall have you serve as the understudy.

198
00:17:41,540 --> 00:17:43,460
You shall enter the civil service.

199
00:17:44,360 --> 00:17:46,300
I must not admit you to the Club

200
00:17:46,920 --> 00:17:49,180
unless you prove yourself worthy.

201
00:17:49,600 --> 00:17:53,020
Else it will be said that I favour my kin.

202
00:17:53,820 --> 00:17:56,700
However,
upon seeing you dance last time,

203
00:17:56,920 --> 00:17:59,140
Phraya Dechanarong
was much impressed.

204
00:18:05,880 --> 00:18:08,420
But I have no wish to serve
in the civil service.

205
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:11,820
I wish to tend the house,
keep my mother company,

206
00:18:12,240 --> 00:18:14,060
and be of assistance to you.

207
00:18:14,740 --> 00:18:15,980
That is better than all else.

208
00:18:17,700 --> 00:18:19,500
Not to enter the civil service?

209
00:18:20,040 --> 00:18:22,740
To sit at home in idleness?

210
00:18:23,240 --> 00:18:27,020
How could you ever be a match
for Phraya Dechanarong's daughter?

211
00:18:28,340 --> 00:18:30,320
You are no longer a child.

212
00:18:30,460 --> 00:18:33,100
Do not be petulant.

213
00:18:35,380 --> 00:18:38,220
This matter lies far in the future.

214
00:18:39,420 --> 00:18:41,380
We shall speak of it another time.

215
00:18:42,400 --> 00:18:43,350
Rit,

216
00:18:43,660 --> 00:18:45,060
continue your meal.

217
00:18:45,280 --> 00:18:46,900
When you have finished,

218
00:18:47,440 --> 00:18:51,060
come and have dessert with me
in the back garden.

219
00:18:52,220 --> 00:18:53,820
It is because you indulge him so

220
00:18:54,400 --> 00:18:56,160
that your son has grown spoiled

221
00:18:56,200 --> 00:18:57,660
and remains a child.

222
00:18:58,180 --> 00:19:00,340
As though
he were still a babe in arms.

223
00:19:00,740 --> 00:19:02,940
As wilful as a child.

224
00:19:04,220 --> 00:19:06,380
You may behave so with others,

225
00:19:06,420 --> 00:19:08,100
but not with your father.

226
00:19:08,140 --> 00:19:10,420
It is time you acted like a grown man.

227
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:15,580
My dear, that will do.

228
00:19:16,060 --> 00:19:17,700
And you as well.

229
00:19:17,980 --> 00:19:19,940
Do not be so wilful.

230
00:19:20,620 --> 00:19:24,540
I asked that Rit enter the civil service,
serve as a royal Khon dancer,

231
00:19:25,080 --> 00:19:28,300
and marry Phraya Dechanarong's daughter.

232
00:19:28,900 --> 00:19:30,460
Such is the plan.

233
00:19:30,740 --> 00:19:32,260
There shall be no change.

234
00:19:43,180 --> 00:19:44,340
Your father

235
00:19:44,380 --> 00:19:46,740
has been ill-tempered of late.

236
00:19:47,400 --> 00:19:49,940
He is much occupied with matters
both public and private.

237
00:19:51,220 --> 00:19:52,660
Do not take it to heart, my son.

238
00:19:53,120 --> 00:19:55,420
Let me speak with him.

239
00:20:05,020 --> 00:20:06,700
Master Rit will be here shortly.

240
00:20:07,260 --> 00:20:09,370
Thank you.

241
00:20:24,160 --> 00:20:25,460
What is the matter, Saen?

242
00:20:27,240 --> 00:20:29,340
You seem uneasy.

243
00:20:31,440 --> 00:20:32,680
It is nothing at all, Master.

244
00:20:34,640 --> 00:20:36,820
Are you displeased that

245
00:20:37,420 --> 00:20:40,180
I accepted my brother's invitation
this evening?

246
00:20:42,020 --> 00:20:44,940
I fear it may upset your stomach.

247
00:20:47,760 --> 00:20:49,660
The liquor here
is quite different from that abroad.

248
00:20:50,620 --> 00:20:53,220
It has been a long while
since you last had Siamese liquor.

249
00:20:55,180 --> 00:20:56,660
I fear that...

250
00:20:56,700 --> 00:20:57,740
Do you worry for me?

251
00:21:03,500 --> 00:21:05,260
You need not worry for me, Saen.

252
00:21:06,100 --> 00:21:08,480
Though I have been long absent,

253
00:21:09,360 --> 00:21:11,620
I have not forgotten all.

254
00:21:25,760 --> 00:21:27,660
After so long abroad,

255
00:21:27,900 --> 00:21:29,940
you must have forgotten
the taste of Siamese liquor.

256
00:21:32,740 --> 00:21:34,020
I shall prove you wrong.

257
00:22:06,780 --> 00:22:07,840
There was something

258
00:22:09,000 --> 00:22:11,420
I had meant to ask you...

259
00:22:12,020 --> 00:22:13,500
On that day...

260
00:22:14,320 --> 00:22:17,420
was it Saen who played Thotsakan?

261
00:22:17,960 --> 00:22:20,900
And... You!

262
00:22:22,020 --> 00:22:23,740
Where have you been?

263
00:22:34,100 --> 00:22:34,950
Rak.
